Package sac.graph

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ClosedSet
    Common interface for closed graph states containers.
    GraphState
    An abstract state in some graph search problem.
    OpenSet
    Common interface for containers with open states.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AStar
    A* algorithm.
    BestFirstSearch
    Best First Search algorithm.
    BreadthFirstSearch
    Breadth First Search algorithm.
    ClosedSetAsHashMap
    Closed set implementation via: java.util.HashMap.
    ClosedSetAsTreeMap
    Closed set implementation via: java.util.TreeSet.
    ConsoleGraphSearchMonitor
    Implementation of monitor with System.out console as output.
    DepthFirstSearch
    Depth First Search algorithm.
    Dijkstra
    Dijkstra's algorithm.
    GraphicalGraphSearchMonitor
    Implementation of monitor with graphical charts as output (charts generated by jfreechart software, http://www.jfree.org/jfreechart/).
    GraphSearchAlgorithm
    Abstract graph search algorithm.
    GraphSearchConfigurator
    Set of configuration settings for graph searches.
    GraphSearchMonitor
    Abstract monitor of graph search algorithm.
    GraphStateImpl
    Abstract partial implementation of GraphState interface.
    GraphStateImpl.GFunction
    Default implementation of the true cost function (g function).
    IterativeDeepeningAStar
    IDA* algorithm.
    OpenSetAsPriorityQueue
    Open set implementation via: java.util.PriorityQueue and java.util.HashMap.
    OpenSetAsPriorityQueueFastContains
    Open set implementation via: java.util.PriorityQueue and java.util.HashMap.
    OpenSetAsPriorityQueueFastContainsFastReplace
    Open set implementation via: own-implementation of binary heap (faster replaces) and java.util.HashMap.
    OpenSetImpl
    Abstract initial implementation of open set.
